# Alogyan — System Architecture

> Stack: Next.js · Node.js · Firebase Firestore · Firebase Auth · Redis

---

## 1. Project Classification

| Dimension | Classification | Rationale |
|-----------|---------------|-----------|
| Scale | **SaaS (1K–100K users)** | Growing teacher platform, not a startup MVP |
| Architecture | **Modular Monolith** | 1–5 dev team; microservices not justified |
| Domain Complexity | **Medium** | CRUD-heavy + business rules (fee calc, attendance %) |
| Real-time need | **Low** | Eventual consistency acceptable; polling acceptable |
| Pattern | **Partial DDD + Repository** | Rich entities, clear module boundaries |

---

